.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, collecting, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, may, january, october
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, snooker, whist
4 different pets are kept: fish, guinea-pig, pony, rabbit
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 2. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person playing go##8
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in december is not the owner of the pony##6
 6. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the right of the person playing mah-jongg##5
10. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
12. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
13. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person drinking tea##1
15. the person who's hobby is board-games is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
16. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
17. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking coffee##1
18. the person drinking coffee is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
19. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's hobby is collecting##6
20. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
21. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | coffee    | mirinda    | almond-milk | tea            |
| Hobby         | camping   | collecting | board-games | skydiving      |
| Birthday           | january   | december   | may | october |
| Game   | mah-jongg | snooker     | whist     | go           |
| Pet           | pony      | guinea-pig | fish        | rabbit         |

